    <title>mysql在ubuntu上的安装</title>
    <link href="/2023/12/27/mysql%E5%9C%A8ubuntu%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/"/>
    <url>/2023/12/27/mysql%E5%9C%A8ubuntu%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="mysql在ubuntu上的安装"><a href="#mysql在ubuntu上的安装" class="headerlink" title="mysql在ubuntu上的安装"></a>mysql在ubuntu上的安装</h1><blockquote><p>环境:kubuntu23.04,kde5.27,安装默认mysql8</p></blockquote><h2 id="默认安装情况下"><a href="#默认安装情况下" class="headerlink" title="默认安装情况下"></a>默认安装情况下</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">安装mysql</span><br><br>sudo apt install mysql-server<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">验证安装</span><br><br>sudo systemctl mysql-server<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">启动</span><br><br>sudo /etc/init.d/mysql start<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">配置安全设置,默认为中等强度,8位长度,包含大小写字母和特殊字符,例如@Root314</span><br><br>sudo mysql_secure_installation<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>安全设置按提示操作即可,此时已经安装好了mysql,可以使用</p><p>sudo mysql -u root -p</p><p>并输入密码来查看是否可以正常连接</p><h2 id="没有设定root用户密码-需要新建用户"><a href="#没有设定root用户密码-需要新建用户" class="headerlink" title="没有设定root用户密码&#x2F;需要新建用户"></a>没有设定root用户密码&#x2F;需要新建用户</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs shell"><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">查看默认安装的mysql的用户名和密码</span><br><br>sudo cat /etc/mysql/debian.cnf<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">登录mysql用户,并输入刚才查到的密码</span><br><br>mysql -u debian-sys-maint -p<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">进入mysql</span><br><br>use mysql<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">刷新权限；</span><br><br>flush privileges;<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">修改用户名和密码；</span><br><br>ALTER USER &#x27;root&#x27;@&#x27;localhost&#x27; IDENTIFIED WITH caching_sha2_password BY &#x27;@Root314&#x27;;<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">刷新权限</span><br><br>flush privileges;<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">退出</span><br><br>quit;<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">重启 MySQL</span><br><br>service mysql restart;<br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_"></span><br><span class="hljs-meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">进入 MySQL ,回车后输入自己修改后的密码即可</span><br><br>msql -u root -p;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
